10-14T08:10:23.000Z","msg":"你咪反問下佢，如果喺而家咁嘅市道（6月前）白手起家，有冇可能喺香港買到層樓LOL，個問題可以差唔多...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。如果佢講共享大灣榮耀+真係肯喺大陸買樓嘅話我佩服佢添Lol（前提佢無喺香港呃公屋綜援）"},{"pid":"1409803c66820acdd4bdd77b0dff38011f2b371a","tid":1653131,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:13:19.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書"}]}